Cell.Text: I knew that stupid kid would try and find a way to weasel out of his debt. | Look, this is really simple. I lent him some gold, he promised to pay me back and now he says he's broke. End of story.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireBranchTopic: I wanted to talk about Shadr's debt.

Cell.Text: [S] All right, all right. I guess I made enough from him shipment. No need to waste any more time threatening a stable hand. | Tell Shadr he doesn't owe me anything.
I don't care, a deal's a deal.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireBranchTopic01: You and I both know this is a setup. (Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] Don't know why you'd help a stranger like that, but a septim's a septim... don't care where it comes from. | You can tell Shadr his debt's been paid.
You don't have enough gold to pay it off, and I'm not cutting any deals.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireBranchTopic02: I'll just pay it off for him. ( Gold)

Cell.Text: [S] All right, all right! Take it easy. No idea why you'd care about a stranger so much, but this isn't worth a fight. | Tell Shadr I'm forgetting about his debt.
Ha ha! Are you kidding me? I've got the entire Thieves Guild at my back. What've you got?

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireBranchTopic03: Drop the debt or answer to me. (Intimidate)

Cell.Text: G|You can go back and forth all you want, he just needs to pay.
Back off, this action's all mine. No room for anyone else in the Guild on this one.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGBranchTopic: I wanted to ask you about Shadr's debt.

Cell.Text: Why should I bother? I've already made a bunch of coin off of his shipment, so anything else I squeeze out of him would be a bonus. | Oh... wait a second. I see what this is. You want me to cut you in or you'll rat me out to Brynjolf. | Tell you what. I'll give you a share right now if you forget the whole thing.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGBranchTopic01: Do me a favor and drop the debt.

Cell.Text: [S] Now you're talking. | Oh, if you see Shadr, remind him he still owes me that debt.
[S] Woah, woah. Calm down. Let's just think about this for a moment. | Sigh. You win. Tell Shadr he can forget the debt.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGBranchTopic03: Forget it, I'm going to speak to Brynjolf.

Cell.Text: Oh, you heard about that, huh? Uh, sorry boss. I was going to speak to Delvin about cutting the Guild in, but I forgot. | You aren't angry about it, right?

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGLeaderBranchTopic: I wanted to talk to you about Shadr's debt.

Cell.Text: [S] Yeah, I figured it would be like that. Here you go.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGLeaderBranchTopic01: Cut me into the deal, and I'll forget about it.

Cell.Text: [S] I got the message. Consider it forgotten, boss.

Node.Caption: FFRiften22SapphireTGLeaderBranchTopic02: Forget the debt with Shadr or you're out.
